<li id="cite_note-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Charles M. Nielsen to Heber Grant, February 10, 1898, in Dan Vogel, ed., <i>Early Mormon Documents</i> (Salt Lake City, Utah: Signature Books, 1998), 2: 476; <i><a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Church_(Joseph_Smith)" class="mw-redirect" title="History of the Church (Joseph Smith)">History of the Church</a></i> 1:39–42.</span>
