<li id="cite_note-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFVogel2004" class="citation book cs1">Vogel, Dan (2004). <i>Joseph Smith: The Making of a Prophet</i>. Salt Lake City: Signature Books. p.&#160;548. <a href="/wiki/ASIN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ASIN (identifier)">ASIN</a>&#160;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07NTCYDQB">B07NTCYDQB</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Joseph+Smith%3A+The+Making+of+a+Prophet&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pages=548&amp;rft.pub=Signature+Books&amp;rft.date=2004&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB07NTCYDQB%23id-name%3DASIN&amp;rft.aulast=Vogel&amp;rft.aufirst=Dan&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOliver+Cowdery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
