<li id="cite_note-Anderson1992-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Anderson1992_17-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFAndersonLudlow1992" class="citation book cs1">Anderson, Richard; Ludlow, Daniel (1992). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://archive.bookofmormoncentral.org/node/568"><i>Encyclopedia of Mormonism</i></a>. New York: Macmillan. pp.&#160;335–340. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780029040409" title="Special:BookSources/9780029040409"><bdi>9780029040409</bdi></a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">January 30,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Encyclopedia+of+Mormonism&amp;rft.place=New+York&amp;rft.pages=335-340&amp;rft.pub=Macmillan&amp;rft.date=1992&amp;rft.isbn=9780029040409&amp;rft.aulast=Anderson&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rft.au=Ludlow%2C+Daniel&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Farchive.bookofmormoncentral.org%2Fnode%2F568&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOliver+Cowdery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
