<li id="cite_note-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">See Mark L. Staker, "Raising Money in Righteousness: Oliver Cowdery as Banker," in <i>Days Never to Be Forgotten: Oliver Cowdery</i>, ed. Alexander L. Baugh (Provo, UT: Religious Studies Center, Brigham Young University, 2009), 143–254.</span>
