<li id="cite_note-19"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">W. W. Phelps to Oliver Cowdery, December 25, 1834, <i>EMD</i>, 3: 28</span>
