<li id="cite_note-28"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-28">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite class="citation web cs1"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.olivercowdery.com/smithhome/1838Sent.htm">"Document Showing The Testimony ... on the Trial of Joseph Smith, Jr"</a>. <i>olivercowdery.com</i>. Joseph Smith's History Vault. <q>(Washington D. C.: Blair &amp; Rives, 1841)</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=olivercowdery.com&amp;rft.atitle=Document+Showing+The+Testimony+...+on+the+Trial+of+Joseph+Smith%2C+Jr.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.olivercowdery.com%2Fsmithhome%2F1838Sent.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOliver+Cowdery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
