<li id="cite_note-Testimony_of_Jacob_Gates-38"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Testimony_of_Jacob_Gates_38-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFScott_H._Faulring" class="citation cs2">Scott H. Faulring, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20111021025608/http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/transcripts/?id=50"><i>The Return of Oliver Cowdery</i></a>, <a href="/wiki/Neal_A._Maxwell_Institute_for_Religious_Scholarship" class="mw-redirect" title="Neal A. Maxwell Institute for Religious Scholarship">Maxwell Institute</a>, archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/publications/transcripts/?id=50">the original</a> on October 21, 2011<span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved <span class="nowrap">April 10,</span> 2012</span></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+Return+of+Oliver+Cowdery&amp;rft.pub=Maxwell+Institute&amp;rft.au=Scott+H.+Faulring&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fmaxwellinstitute.byu.edu%2Fpublications%2Ftranscripts%2F%3Fid%3D50&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOliver+Cowdery" class="Z3988"></span>; <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFGates1912" class="citation book cs1">Gates, Jacob F. (March 1912). "Testimony of Jacob Gates". <i>Improvement Era 15</i>. p.&#160;92.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.atitle=Testimony+of+Jacob+Gates&amp;rft.btitle=Improvement+Era+15&amp;rft.pages=92&amp;rft.date=1912-03&amp;rft.aulast=Gates&amp;rft.aufirst=Jacob+F.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AOliver+Cowdery" class="Z3988"></span></span>
