<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Joseph_Smith" title="Joseph Smith">J. Smith</a> (1829–44)<sup id="cite_ref-not12_52-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-not12-52">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Cowdery</a> (1829–38)<sup id="cite_ref-not12_52-1" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-not12-52">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-excommunication_53-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-excommunication-53">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>
