<li><a href="/wiki/Thomas_B._Marsh" title="Thomas B. Marsh">Marsh</a> (1835–39)<sup id="cite_ref-excommunication_53-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-excommunication-53">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/David_W._Patten" title="David W. Patten">Patten</a> (1835–38)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">B. Young Sr.</a> (1835–77)</li>
